collections.name: Helena Sarin And Her Band
collections.description: In Helena Sarin and Her Band, the artist presents her riff on two distinct musical forms: the intimate jazz band and the big band. Jazz, in particular, has been a key source of inspiration for Sarin, filling her studio with vibrant energy and creative spontaneity. Here, she pays tribute to these art forms, capturing their spirit in her work. Sarin notes, “To paraphrase Basquiat, I wanted to be a jazz musician, but I couldn’t play well; so my code became my music.”

collections.name: <OLD>ETOdots
collections.description:
In Japan there is a culture that came from China called "ETO".
This is a system in which 12 different creatures are assigned according to the year of birth.
The 12 creatures are rat, cow(ox), tiger, rabbit, dragon, snake, horse, sheep, monkey, chicken, dog, and boar.
By the way, the year 2025 will be the year of the snake.

Please try to find the "ETO" that corresponds to your year of birth.

The “ETO” goes around in a 12-year cycle
Year of the Rat: 1936, 1948, ..., 2020
Year of the Ox: 1937, 1949, ..., 2021
Year of the Tiger: 1938, 1950, ..., 2022
Year of the Rabbit: 1939, 1951, ..., 2023
Year of the Dragon: 1940, 1952, ..., 2024
Year of the Snake: 1941, 1953, ..., 2025
Year of the Horse: 1942, 1954, ..., 2014
Year of the Sheep: 1943, 1955, ..., 2015
Year of the Monkey: 1944, 1956, ..., 2016
Year of the Chicken: 1945, 1957, ..., 2017
Year of the Dog: 1946, 1958, ..., 2018
Year of the Wild Boar: 1947, 1959, ..., 2019

collections.name: Interior Masks
collections.description:
The Interior Masks explore psychological archetypes and the dualism between strength and weakness. Each NFT is a reflection of the soul, inspired by Lowen's signature types, mythology and futuristic art.

These works combine organic and inorganic materials – leather, metal, stone – creating enigmatic faces that act as mirrors of the unconscious. Empty eyes, engravings and ritual ornaments evoke the passage between interior dimensions, symbols of wisdom, transformation and collective memory.

Each mask is a portal to one's own introspection. Who will tell your story?

SPACED is an NFT-based membership granting access to hidden retreats, premium resorts & futuristic sanctuaries—spaces collectively designed, funded and built by its members and the SPACED team - a bunch of architects, builders, engineers & dreamers pushing the envelope in destination development.

The SPACED Genesis Collection is the foundation of an evolving global network. As a Genesis member, you gain lifetime access to our first development and all future locations. This is your key to a movement that builds exclusive spaces around the world.

Your Genesis tokens—and all future SPACED tokens—are backed by the success of the real-world tourism assets they help develop. This ensures long-term value stability, reducing hype-driven volatility should you wish to sell.
